APPENDIX E: EVOLUTION OF CONFIDENCE VALUES DURING AN EPISODE
This appendix presents the expanded version of the results shown in Section 4.4. The aim is to show the how the confidence values dynamically change over the duration of an episode and show the presence of explicit peaks and troughs in many games. Here, it's important to note that the apparent periodicity observed in some graphs is not because of the nature of the confidences learnt but is instead due to the periodic nature of the games themselves.
